# NestJS (dnd-api)

1. Skill global `nestjs` + local `nestjs-bounded-context`.
2. **Catalog** `src/catalog/` — thin, GET only (`catalog-thin-layer`).
3. **Identity** `src/identity/` · **Game** `src/game/` — handlers/application.
4. Controllers finos; catálogo sem POST/PATCH/DELETE em `phb_*`.
5. Config `@nestjs/config`; `.env` nunca commitado.
